Here is a demo of how one can store passwords in cyphertext.

The code in the "ec" script is intended to be inspiration.

The contents in the "gpg" directory are a small sample of actual
secrets which I have uploaded with the goal of demonstrating the
trust I place in GPG. Permission is hereby granted to read, use,
modify, and redistribute the cipher text ....

